---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="页面未找到 - 立刷POS" currentPath="/" description="您访问的页面不存在，请返回立刷POS官网首页。">
	<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white py-20">
		<div class="relative z-10 max-w-xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-blue-100 mb-6">
				<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.172 16.172a4 4 0 015.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
				</svg>
			</div>

			<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">哎呀，页面走丢了</h1>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed">您访问的页面可能已被移除、名称已更改，或暂时不可用。</p>

			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
				<a href="/" class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20">
					<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-4 0a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1"></path></svg>
					返回首页
				</a>
				<a href="javascript:void(0)" data-apply="simple" data-source="404页面" class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border-2 border-gray-200 text-gray-700 hover:border-blue-300 hover:text-blue-600 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-colors">
					<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path></svg>
					联系客服
				</a>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100">
				<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">或者您可能在找：</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
					<a href="/products" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium hover:underline">产品中心</a>
					<span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
					<a href="/news" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium hover:underline">资讯指南</a>
					<span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
					<a href="/about" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium hover:underline">关于我们</a>
					<span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
					<a href="/news/pos-guide-2026" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium hover:underline">POS办理指南</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
